data_table.description: Frequently Used Cardiovascular Risk Factors (a.k.a. "Workthru"), Offspring, Exam 1 - Exam 9. This purpose of this dataset is to: 1) Abstract and rename frequently used variables across exams for ease of use; 2) Standardize units across exams; 3) Standardize calculated variables across exams; 4) Incorporate variable value corrections reported over several years.
